title: Stock Intrinsic Value

api_list.name: Get Intrinsic Value
api_list.description: This endpoint will return back specific stock's Intrinsic Value and details
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://stock-intrinsic-value.p.rapidapi.com/stock/{stockid}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "stock-intrinsic-value.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
